House Resolution 594
By: Representative Parrish of the 158th
A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life and memory of David Lamar Beecher, Sr.; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, the State of Georgia mourns the loss of one of its most distinguished citizens
3 with the passing of David Lamar Beecher, Sr., on March, 6, 2025; and
4 WHEREAS, David Lamar Beecher, Sr., born in 1941, was a beloved son of Fate and Sarah
5 Beecher; and
6 WHEREAS, since 1970, David Lamar Beecher, Sr., has been a beloved member of the David
7 Emmanuel Academy Community; and
8 WHEREAS, his unwavering and principled guidance inspired his faculty and staff, as well
9 as set an example for countless students; and
10 WHEREAS, a man of deep and abiding faith, David Lamar Beecher, Sr., was an active
11 member of Olney Primitive Baptist Church; and
